This repository contains code for the research paper

**Necessary and Sufficient Conditions for Existence and Uniqueness of Recursive Utilities**

by Jaroslav Boroviƒçka and John Stachurski.

The paper is available [via arXiv](https://arxiv.org/abs/1710.06526).

The code is written in Python and is currently being implemented in MATLAB. This
directory will contain the MATLAB implementation.

The ssy_ files in /long_run_risk/src are currently being implemented along with
the associated Jupyter notebooks. After that the by_ files will be implemented.
Finally the /constant_vol and /markov_switching directories will be addressed.

Please visit this repository periodically for updates.
